this discourse of female madness influenced ophelia 's representation on stage from the 1660s , when the appearance of actresses in the english theatres first began to introduce " new meanings and subversive tensions " into the role : " the most celebrated of the actresses who played ophelia were those whom rumor credited with disappointments in love."showalter ( 1985 , 80 , 81 ) .

